This directory contains the full source of OPIUM, which is an open-source
pseudopotential generation program.

Please see the file COPYING for copying conditions.

Please see the files in the doc/ directory for more information.

See the file INSTALL for compilation and installation instructions,

Additional information can be found on the OPIUM website: http://opium.sourceforge.net

